## ðŸ“š Examples Included

After running `kalibr-connect examples`, youâ€™ll get:

- `basic_kalibr_example.py` â€“ simple function-level demo  
- `enhanced_kalibr_example.py` â€“ full app with sessions, uploads, and streaming  

