## ðŸ”¥ Why Kalibr?

Without Kalibr:
- Learn 4 model specs  
- Maintain 4 codebases  
- Duplicate effort  

With Kalibr:
- One Python function  
- Four schemas generated automatically  
- Deploy anywhere  

